-- Australia Defeats Sri Lanka to Sweep Test Cricket Series 3-0
-- B y   D a n   B a y n e s
-- 2013-01-06T04:52:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-06/australia-defeats-sri-lanka-to-sweep-test-cricket-series-3-0.html
Australia beat Sri Lanka by five
wickets in their third cricket Test in Sydney to sweep the
series 3-0.  Retiring batsman  Mike Hussey  hit 27 not out to help guide
Australia to the victory target following the tea break after
the home team slipped to 108-4 chasing 141 on day four. Sri
Lanka was earlier dismissed for 278 in its second innings.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Baynes at 
 dbaynes@bloomberg.net  